title: Diamond Toplaner looking for team
body:
Hello,
I'm a german Diamondelo Toplaner and I am currently looking for a team for 5n5 ranked.
I preffer a german team but an english team is fine for me too although my english is not that good.
Everyone in that team should be at least Diamondelo if you want me to join.
Just post under this post if you interested to play with me :)
Best wishes
Rayengo247
